channel.title: MJ IN THE MIX
channel.itunes:title: Michael Joseph
channel.itunes:subtitle: Live Performances Sets Mixes and Remixes by Michael Joseph
channel.itunes:author: IN THE MIX with Michael Joseph
channel.itunes:summary: Hey-Hey and welcome to the "In The Mix with Michael Joseph" Podcast. The many different episodes here are a mix between Live Sets, Studio Recordings, Live Performances, Mixes and Remixes by Michael Joseph. There are different styles of mixes and music. Some are Hip Hop and others Electronic music. It's all about Dancing. There will be new updates often. MJ both performs as a live vocal act and DJs all over the United States. To find out more about MJ, go to www.immj.com where you can find links to his myspace, facebook and twitter.

item.title: Michael Joseph - The Hot Summer Sun Tour 2012 Mix (Part 1 of 3)
item.itunes:author: Michael Joseph (MC / DJ / MJ)
item.itunes:subtitle: The Hot Summer Sun Tour 2012 Mix (Part 1 of 3)
item.itunes:summary: Back for it's 5th year, The Hot Summer Sun Tour drops it's summer mix in 3 parts for 2012. MC / DJ Michael Joseph brings the summer sound track in 3 parts ... 1 to kick off the summer season on the memorial day weekend. 2 to keep the party rollin' for July. and 3 one last party punch for the Labor day weekend.
